refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
stringrawurlencode stringdizge
Belirtilen dizgeye RFC 1738'e uygun URL kodlaması uygular.

  &reftitle.examples;



    - Bir FTP URL'sinde parola belirtmek


<?php
echo '<a href="ftp://user:', rawurlencode('foo @+%/'),
     '@ftp.example.com/x.txt">';
?>


    &example.outputs;


<a href="ftp://user:foo%20%40%2B%25%2F@ftp.example.com/x.txt">






   Bilgiyi URL'nin PATH_INFO bileşeninde aktarırsanız:




    - Başka bir rawurlencode örneği


<?php
echo '<a href="http://example.com/department_list_script/',
    rawurlencode('sales and marketing/Miami'), '">';
?>


    &example.outputs;


<a href="http://example.com/department_list_script/sales%20and%20marketing%2FMiami">
